children.text: Enough Said spoken word series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on January 23, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by Neil Wiernick and Fortner Anderson. Open mic/supporting performances by Joelle Ciona, Fluffy Pagan Echoes (Victoria Stanton, Scott Duncan, Vincent Tinguely), Ian Stephens, Justin McGrail, and more.
